  </sponsors>
  <source>Abgenix</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Trial evaluating the improvement in survival at 180 days of two therapies (Atgam versus
      ABX-CBL, a monoclonal antibody) in patients with acute graft versus host disease that does
      not respond to steroid therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
